description.p:
In the design assistance system of the invention, the generation section generates a device list display screen displaying a list of device components representing slave devices which can be newly joined to a network system under design and also generates a design assistance GUI containing a topology display screen and the device list display screen, so that

if operations to select any one of the device components enumerated on the device list display screen are performed by the user,

the generation section may change the aspect of displaying the device components representing the slave devices to which the slave device represented by the device component selected on the device list display screen cannot be connected among the device components composing the topology display screen.

In the design assistance system of the invention, the generation section generates a device list display screen displaying a list of device components representing slave devices which can be newly joined to a network system under design and also generates a design assistance GUI containing a topology display screen and the device list display screen, so that

if operations to select any one of the device components enumerated on the topology display screen are performed by the user,

the generation section may change the aspect of displaying the device components representing the slave devices to which the slave device represented by the device component selected on the topology display screen cannot be connected among the device components enumerated on the device list display screen.

claim.claim-text:
The design assistance system according to claim 1 or 2, wherein the generation section generates a device list display screen displaying a list of the device components representing the slave devices which are configured to be newly joined to the network system under design and also generates a design assistance GUI containing a topology display screen and the device list display screen, so that

if operations to select any one of the device components enumerated on the device list display screen are performed by the user,

the generation section changes the aspect of displaying the device components representing the slave devices to which the slave device represented by the device component selected on the device list display screen is not configured to be connected among the device components composing the topology display screen.

The design assistance system according to any one of claims 1 to 3, wherein the generation section generates a device list display screen displaying a list of the device components representing the slave devices which are configured to be newly joined to the network system under design, and also generates the design assistance GUI containing the topology display screen and the device list display screen, so that

if operations to select any one of the device components composing the topology display screen are performed by the user,

the generation section changes the aspect of displaying the device components representing the slave devices to which the slave device represented by the device component selected on the topology display screen is not configured to be connected among the device components enumerated on the device list display screen.
